Math 110 - Section 3 - Linear Algebra
Instructor: Lek-Heng Lim
Lectures: MWF 11:00am-12:00pm, Room 71 Evans
Course Control Number: 54811
Office: 873 Evans
Office Hours: M 12&ndash;2pm, W 2&ndash;4pm
